{"title":"华夏放歌","authors":["陆圣存"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":10,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"华夏放歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陆圣存"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——有感于邓小平南巡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世纪老人去南巡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"薰风铺来满目春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华夏欢欣惊雷贯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炎黄高歌颂经纶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五岳起舞涌彩霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四海扬波大潮生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方鲲鹏展巨翼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶摇直上傲昆仑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亘古摇篮起苍茫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九州金瀑从天飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万顷琼浆饮铁马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喷出红日扫岚霾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂首东去泼春色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒吼冲霄新宇开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水激穹苍汇大洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旷世风云入怀来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三峡艄公竞风流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛载富庶漫乡都。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩练万里一把瑟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韵弹神州五千秋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝政信民千秋颂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春潮涌动江山荣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旷代天骄换日月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振兴中华唱大风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回归"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——香港、澳门回归感赋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒙耻受辱数百秋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汪洋飘萍二叶舟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一国两制”唤归岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世纪欢歌动九州。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——世纪之交感望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个世纪一肩挑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共同发展竞富饶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下携手揽星月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类合唱和平谣。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}